data.description: Welcome  to this spacious split level home with a finished walkout BASEMENT located in an established neighborhood on the Eastside of town in the desirable Hillcrest area. This home sits on .65 acres on a corner lot. There are 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms with over 2900 sqft of combined living space. Most of the home has been kept original including the beautiful hardwood floors, original bathrooms on the main level, and a gorgeous brick, gas log fireplace in the den. Owners just installed a new water heater and LVP flooring on the main level living area. The walkout basement is completely finished and is where the 4th bedroom, 3rd bathroom, and laundry room are located. Buyer/ Buyer’s agent to verify sqft.
